OL,3,CBelfast Giants secure Elite League
OL,4,Ctitle
OL,6,FThe Belfast Giants have been crowned
OL,7,FElite League champions after defeating
OL,8,Fthe Nottingham Panthers 4-2 at The SSE
OL,9,FArena.
OL,11,FGoals from Mike Lee, Carsen Twarynski,
OL,12,Fand a double from captain David
OL,13,FGoodwin secured a second successive
OL,14,Ftitle for Adam Keefe's side.
OL,16,FThe Giants and Panthers go head-to-
OL,17,Fhead in the second game of their
OL,18,Fdouble-header weekend in front of a
OL,19,Fsold-out crowd at The SSE Arena,
OL,20,FBelfast on Saturday 28 March.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
