OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774879866
OL,3,CBelfast Giants secure Elite League
OL,4,Ctitle
OL,6,FBelfast Giants Captain James Goodwin
OL,7,Fsaid: ""There's a reason Nottingham is
OL,8,Fthe second best team in the league.
OL,10,F"They're a great, great club.
OL,12,F"They made us work for every inch out
OL,13,Fthere.
OL,15,F"So proud of the guys. We're champs,
OL,16,Fwe're so fired up.
OL,26,@oD@HOUrD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
