OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774879866
OL,3,CBelfast Giants secure Elite League
OL,4,Ctitle
OL,6,F" I really believe this organization
OL,7,Fmeans a lot for the city and to be
OL,8,Fable to put on this jersey every night
OL,9,Fand represent this and continue to
OL,10,Fbring people together, it's really
OL,11,Fsomething I don't take lightly.
OL,13,F"Not a day goes by that I take it for
OL,14,Fgranted"
OL,16,FAdam Keefe's side have clinched five
OL,17,Fwins in six seasons and he couldn't be
OL,18,Fmore proud.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774879866
OL,3,CBelfast Giants secure Elite League
OL,4,Ctitle
OL,6,F"My heart is definitely happy. I don't
OL,7,Fthink I could have taken much more of
OL,8,Fthis but I would have been really
OL,9,Fgutted for the guys if they didn't get
OL,10,Fit done tonight because I thought we
OL,11,Fwere fantastic.
OL,13,F"Right from our leader David Goodwin,
OL,14,F2 goals right down throughout the
OL,15,Fwhole lineup.
OL,17,F"I thought, you know, it's special.
OL,19,F"I'm very fortunate to get to coach
OL,20,Fthese guys.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774879866
OL,3,CBelfast Giants secure Elite League
OL,4,Ctitle
OL,6,F"I'm very hard on them at times.I'm
OL,7,Fsure they don't love me, but this is
OL,8,Fwhy we do it, you know.
OL,10,F"I think they understand that as well,
OL,11,Fand the fans and the organisation have
OL,12,Fbeen nothing but fantastic.
OL,14,F"Absolutely incredible, 7000 fans
OL,15,Fevery night here for us, and the
OL,16,Forganisation has given us every tool
OL,17,Fto be successful and to keep on
OL,18,Fwinning.
OL,20,F"There's a difference between winning
OL,21,Fonce and winning year in year out.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
